  # **Figma UI Component Libraries: The Ultimate Guide to Scaling Your Design Process**
  
  [![Anasuri HariPrasad](https://miro.medium.com/v2/da:true/resize:fill:32:32/0*RQHTOxYLFhNMu2Ev)](https://medium.com/@ahprasad.hyd?source=post_page---byline--8fa4dd04a07b---------------------------------------)
  
